<D>__{a guard always wins the surf competition. know why?}
<C>__{together}
<P>__{(robbie and alex)}
<D>__{because concessions kids can't swim!}
<C>__{aokee}
<P>__{(still cleaning)}
<D>__{someday.}
<A>__{they go back into aokee's surf and snack shack.}
